    <name>
      <text>2.3.21 (Spot the scaled graph)</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<div class="center">            <p class="noindent">            </p><p class="noindent">The graph of a function \(y = f(x)\) is given below:<br></p><p class="noindent">{@plot(p,XL,YL,[box, false],[yx_ratio, 1],[axes, solid],[xtics, -10, 2,10],[ytics, -10, 2, 10])@}</p><p class="noindent">Which graph shows the graph of the function \(f({@a*x@})\)?<br></p><p class="noindent">[[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]]&nbsp;<br></p></div><table>
  <tbody><tr>
    <td style="text-align: center;"><span><b>Graph A</b></span></td>
    <td style="text-align: center;"><span><b>Graph B</b></span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="text-align: center;">{@plot(plist[1],XL,YL,[box, false],[yx_ratio, 1],[axes, solid],[xtics, -10, 2,10],[ytics, -10, 2, 10],[alt,"Graph A"])@}</td>
    <td style="text-align: center;">{@plot(plist[2],XL,YL,[box, false],[yx_ratio, 1],[axes, solid],[xtics,-10, 2,10],[ytics, -10, 2, 10],[alt,"Graph B"])@}</td>
  </tr><tr>
    <td style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</td>
    <td style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="text-align: center;"><b>Graph C</b></td>
    <td style="text-align: center;"><b>Graph D</b></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="text-align: center;">{@plot(plist[3],XL,YL,[box, false],[yx_ratio, 1],[axes, solid],[xtics, -10, 2, 10],[ytics, -10, 2, 10],[alt,"Graph C"])@}</td>
    <td style="text-align: center;">{@plot(plist[4],XL,YL,[box, false],[yx_ratio, 1],[axes, solid],[xtics, -10, 2, 10],[ytics, -10, 2, 10],[alt,"Graph D"])@}</td>
  </tr>
</tbody></table><p><br></p>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p class="noindent">The graph of \(f(ax)\) is the graph of \(f(x)\) compressed horizontally if \(a&gt;1\) and, if \(a&lt;-1\), reflected across the \(y\)-axis and compressed horizontally.<br></p>]]></text>
    </generalfeedback>
